reviewText: This hilarious sitcom that ran on CBS from 1993-99 about a nasaly nanny from Flushing, NY caring for 3 Park Avenue kids who constantly clashing with the snootty patooty C.C.(Lauren Lane), plus you get to see it complete and uncut without all those deleted scenes you'd get in reruns on Antenna-TV, TV Land, Lifetime, Hallmark Channel, and now THE NANNY will be coming to Cozi-TV in the Fall of 2017.
pretty good, very funny, but political at times
I love this show, it's a great series!

I bought all  6 season of the show and you will fall in love with every character in this show , you will laugh your butt off
